comment._content: I am lucky to be the owner of an original blueprint book of when this aereoplane was being developed by curtiss.Renamed curtiss wright.Images of this plane are very scarce.I have images of this book on here.Check it out.I would be happy to send more to you.This book is rare.I think there used to be a factory here in Batavia NY on harvestor ave.You never know what youll find in the trash...Dan Cherry
